nearly%20six%20years%2C%20then%20joined%20the%20CIA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDuring%20these%20high-stress%20jobs%2C%20he%20was%20in%20a%20nearly%20constant%20fight-or-flight%20mode.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20he%20left%2C%20he%20struggled%20to%20adapt%20to%20a%20normal%20life.%20He%20says%20a%20psychedelic%20experience%20helped.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Shawn%20Ryan%2C%20a%20former%20Navy%20SEAL%20and%20CIA%20contractor%2C%20and%20host%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BShawn%20Ryan%20Show.%26quot%3B%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Ryan%20is%20not%20a%20medical%20professional.%20Psilocybin%20is%20illegal%20in%20the%20US%20federally%20and%20in%20most%20states.%20There%20is%20no%20medical%20consensus%20about%20whether%20it%20has%20benefits%2C%20including%20those%20described%20below%2C%20and%20the%20drug%20comes%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fare-magic-mushrooms-dangerous-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Erisks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-navy-seals-actually-work-shawn-ryan-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20Navy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20wasn't%20ready%20for%20what%20came%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-navy-seal-military-morning-routine-helps-him-in-business-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeen%20a%20SEAL%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20five%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20contractor%20with%20the%20CIA.%20The%20tempo%20stayed%20high.%20I%20did%2060%20days%20on%2C%2060%20days%20off%2C%20sometimes%2045%20and%2045.%20I%20was%20still%20running%20hard%2C%20living%20in%20fight-or-flight%20mode.%20When%20that%20ended%2C%20I%20crashed%E2%80%94hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20slow%20down.%20I%20wasn't%20used%20to%20dealing%20with%20normal%20life.%20All%20I%20knew%20was%20intensity.%20I%20needed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-drugs-do-to-your-brain-2015-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadrenaline%20hit%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20I%20couldn't%20get%20it%20from%20missions%20anymore%2C%20I%20found%20other%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20into%20sleeping%20pills.%20Ambien%2C%20Valium%2C%20Xanax%2C%20Lorazepam%20%E2%80%94%20you%20name%20it%2C%20I%20was%20taking%20it.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20I%20was%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopioid-overdoses-in-the-us-are-surging-with-the-pandemic-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopiates%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20hydrocodone%20and%20tramadol.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20country%20and%20started%20living%20in%20Medell%C3%ADn%2C%20Colombia.%20That's%20where%20I%20got%20really%20into%20cocaine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20go%20into%20the%20worst%20neighborhoods%20I%20could%20find%20to%20score.%20I%20didn't%20want%20it%20easy%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20risk%2C%20to%20feel%20something.%20When%20that%20got%20boring%2C%20I'd%20go%20to%20another%20country%20and%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20lowest%20point%2C%20I%20was%20drinking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Fsigns-of-alcoholism%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20fifths%20of%20vodka%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20day.%20I'd%20wake%20up%20with%20mini%20bottles%20stashed%20all%20around%20the%20house%20%E2%80%94%20under%20pillows%2C%20in%20drawers%2C%20in%20the%20car%2C%20in%20my%20coat%20pockets.%20After%20dinner%2C%20I'd%20go%20to%20the%20freezer%2C%20pull%20out%20a%20bottle%2C%20and%20that's%20how%20I'd%20wash%20down%20my%20sleep%20meds.%20Except%20by%20the%20end%2C%20they%20didn't%20even%20put%20me%20to%20sleep%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20I'd%20take%20a%20stimulant%20%E2%80%94%20Adderall%20or%20something%20else%20%E2%80%94%20to%20start%20the%20cycle%20again.%20That%20was%20my%20life.%20It%20went%20on%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e89766b0-5394-4b88-b8b5-1baa3de103db%5C%22%3EThe%20'death%20experience'%20that%20changed%20my%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20hit%20a%20point%20where%20I%20knew%20I%20couldn't%20keep%20going.%20A%20friend%20told%20me%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmdma-therapy-maps-lykos-rick-doblin-fda-legalization-trials-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychedelic%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20Ibogaine.%20It's%20a%2012-hour%20experience.%20I%20basically%20watched%20my%20entire%20life%20play%20out%20from%20a%20different%20perspective.%20Every%20memory%2C%20every%20trauma%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Ibogaine%20effects%20wore%20off%2C%20I%20did%20another%20psychedelic%20called%205-MeO-DMT%2C%20sometimes%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BGod%20molecule.%26quot%3B%20The%20trip%20is%20described%20as%20an%20ego%20death%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fayahuasca-dmt-scientists-brain-images-study-psychedelics-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeath%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20most%20intense%2C%20intuitive%20thing%20I've%20ever%20felt.%20I%20came%20out%20of%20it%20seeing%20the%20world%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20feel%20energy%20flowing%20from%20the%20ocean%2C%20onto%20the%20shore%2C%20through%20the%20trees.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20realized%20everything%20is%20connected.%20Everything%20is%20one.%20That%20hit%20me%20in%20a%20way%20nothing%20else%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20came%20back%20from%20that%20psychedelic%20experience%2C%20I%20didn't%20need