items%20we%20buy%2C%20and%20the%20clothes%20we%20wear%2C%20which%2C%20oftentimes%2C%20and%20to%20the%20surprise%20of%20many%20Americans%2C%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-walmart-target-sold-clothes-from-blacklisted-factories-unsafe-wsj-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20in%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20if%20the%20equivalent%20were%20true%2C%20but%20for%20robots%3F%20This%20is%20a%20film%20that%20envisions%20a%20future%20in%20which%20our%20country%20is%20populated%20by%20robots%20from%20another%20country%2C%20brought%20here%20to%20serve%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20memories%20they%20carry%20of%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20asks%20people%20to%20reflect%20on%20how%20they%20treat%20others.%20How%20we%20worry%20about%20being%20oppressed%2C%20but%20in%20fact%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20might%20be%20the%20oppressor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20an%20AI%20filmmaking%20course%20from%20Curious%20Refuge%2C%20which%20helped%20me%20better%20prompt%20these%20tools.%20What's%20interesting%20about%20prompting%20is%20that%20it's%20just%20sort%20of%20churning.%20You're%20pulling%20a%20slot%20machine%20over%20and%20over%20again.%20I%20generated%20thousands%20of%20robots%20to%20get%20the%20ones%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20experiment.%20Ask%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Brobot-horse%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20style%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguillermo-del-toro-martin-scorsese-criticism-movie-length-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuillermo%20del%20Toro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20try%20Spielberg%2C%20and%20see%20which%20one%20you%20like%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20a%20mix%20of%20technical%20terms%20and%20descriptive%20verses%20in%20prompting.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20like%20the%20depth%20of%20field%20and%20spatial%20distortion%20of%20a%2028-millimeter%20lens%2C%20so%20I%20often%20include%20%26quot%3B28-millimeter%26quot%3B%20in%20my%20prompts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20a%20mistake%20for%20the%20critics%20of%20AI%20to%20say%20that%20one%20of%20the%20downsides%20of%20AI%20is%20that%20it%20can't%20be%20used%20to%20make%20great%20art.%20I%20think%20this%20film%20is%20pretty%20good.%20I%20feel%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20having%20authored%20it.%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20story%20and%20every%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20the%20right%20to%20profit%20off%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%20is%20clearly%20violating%20intellectual%20property.%20It%20poses%20a%20real%20danger%20of%20displacing%20and%20putting%20people%20out%20of%20work.%20It's%20also%20exacerbating%20climate%20damage%20because%20of%20how%20energy-intensive%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20deeply%20conflicted%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESee%20Hossain's%20full%20movie%20below.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplayer.vimeo.com%2Fapi%2Fplayer.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20title%3D%5C%22Do%20Bangladroids%20Dream%20Of%20Electric%20Tagore%3F%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplayer.vimeo.com%2Fvideo%2F1050152870%3Fbadge%3D0%26autopause%3D0%26player_id%3D0%26app_id%3D58479%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-film-movie-ethics-conflict-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746870301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681ce51ec6ad288d148066a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-film-movie-ethics-conflict-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aleem%20Hossain%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Occidental%20College%2C%20made%20a%20movie%20using%20AI.%20He%20told%20BI%20he%20thinks%20it's%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20good%26quot%3