0Commander%26quot%3B%20are%20meant%20to%20spur%20thought%20and%20imagination%2C%20rather%20than%20create%20a%20surefire%20plan%20to%20defeat%20China.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20depiction%20of%20warfare%20of%20the%20future%2C%20because%20I%20cannot%20predict%20the%20future%20nor%20can%20any%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bae%2C%20a%20former%20Marine%20sergeant%20and%20Iraq%20War%20veteran%20who%20now%20designs%20wargames%20for%20the%20Center%20for%20Naval%20Analyses%20think%20tank.%20%26quot%3BI%20created%20'Littoral%20Commander'%20to%20be%20an%20intellectual%20sandbox%20for%20people%20to%20explore%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20learn%20about%20capabilities.%20How%20these%20capabilities%20work%20and%20what%20challenges%20and%20opportunities%20they%20may%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221058%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20players%20rely%20on%20capability%20cards%20like%20this%20one%20to%20hunt%20for%20their%20enemies%20and%20strike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681bc3e6a466d2b74ab55404%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20players%20rely%20on%20cards%20like%20this%20one%20for%20strike%20and%20reconnaissance%20capabilities.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sebastian%20Bae%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20illustrates%20the%20panoply%20of%20current%20and%20future%20capabilities%20through%20200%20%26quot%3BJoint%20Capability%20Cards%26quot%3B%2C%20complete%20with%20separate%20US%20and%20Chinese%20decks.%20Cards%20include%20drones%2C%20bombers%2C%20cyber%20operations%20and%20signals%20intelligence%2C%20minefields%2C%20special%20forces%20raids%2C%20naval%20gunfire%20and%20other%20extras%20that%20players%20purchase%20using%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20%26quot%3Bcommand%20points.%26quot%3B%20The%20mechanism%20is%20somewhat%20gamey%20%E2%80%94%20battalions%20commanders%20don't%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fb-52-bomber-faces-more-delays-rising-costs-new-upgrades-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EB-52%3C%2Fa%3E%20strikes%20on%20demand%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20practical%20effect%20is%20to%20allow%20players%20to%20experiment%20with%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20capabilities.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20tactical%20leader%2C%20you%20only%20get%20a%20tiny%20sliver%20of%20them%20at%20any%20given%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Bae%20explained.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20wanted%20players%20to%20think%2C%20plan%2C%20and%20assess%20how%20and%20what%20they%20needed%20to%20execute%20their%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinning%20at%20%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20means%20mastering%20a%20few%20key%20variables.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20important%20is%20detecting%20the%20enemy%3A%20as%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20shown%2C%20what%20can%20be%20seen%20can%20be%20destroyed.%20Counters%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20map%20are%20considered%20%26quot%3Bconcealed%3A%26quot%3B%20flipped%20upside%20down%20so%20that%20the%20opponent%20can't%20see%20whether%20they%20are%20an%20infantry%20platoon%2C%20a%20missile%20battery%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20dummy%20piece%20simulating%20the%20fog%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dilemma%20is%20that%20concealed%20units%20can't%20be%20fired%20at.%20Yet%20they%20lose%20concealment%20when%20they%20fire%2C%20or%20when%20their%20locations%20are%20scouted%20by%20enemy%20reconnaissance%20platforms%20or%20ground%20troops.%20Thus%20%26quot%3BLittoral%20Commander%26quot%3B%20becomes%20a%20contest%20of%20hide-and-seek%2C%20where%20the%20combatants%20try%20to%20pinpoint%20enemy%20troops%20for%20missile%20strikes.%20All%20while%20screening%20their%20own%20forces%20from%20enemy%20reconnaissance%20or%2C%20if%20spotted%2C%20changing%20position%20in%20order%20to%20vanish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20shown%2C%20long-range%20fires%20dom